Cyacq Corp said it extended its 80dlr a share tender offer for Cyclops Corp to March 20 fromtoday.    Cyacq was formed by Citicorp Capital Investors Ltd andAudio Video Affiliates INc &lt;AVA> to acquire Cyclops. THe tenderoffer began on February six.    The offer is conditioned upon at least 80 pct of theoutstanding shares and at least 80 pct of the voting securitiesbeing tendered before expiration of the offer.    As of March six, only 353 shares of Cyclops' 4.1 mlnoutstanding shares had been tendered. Reuter&#3;